{"tid":2298983,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"八成人不滿政府表現　陳恒鑌斥檢測中心「倒瀉籮蟹」","createTime":"2020-11-24T12:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T14:26:06.000Z","uid":230530,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd00ee8dc72d17d1f68c64657a0f8c54b20673d","tid":2298983,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"本地疫情反彈，今日（24日）新增共80宗確診個案，當中「跳舞群組」增至187人染疫。團體「青研香港」於21日至23日期間，對6,004名市民進行了有關防疫措施意見的問卷調查，當中有近八成人對政府的抗疫表現感到不滿。身兼團體顧問的立法會議員陳恒鑌，斥政府抗疫工作「做一半唔做一半」，未有檢視不足堵塞漏洞，社區檢測中心更「倒瀉籮蟹」，令市民覺得政府各部門各自為政。<br />\n<br />\n建議強制出入需脫口罩場所要用「安心出行」<br />\n<br />\n另外，受訪者中有91%贊成推行全民強制檢測，另有九成表示贊成政府在疫情期間可加強收集市民的出行紀錄以助追蹤病毒傳播鏈。陳恒鑌提議應在18區設檢測中心，並強制市民出入需要脫下口罩的場所，均以「安心出行」應用程式紀錄行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n國安法出牆啦"},{"pid":"733a21cbc82944c3e125ab70ffec90cd6776a410","tid":2298983,"uid":11291,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:03:01.000Z","msg":"陳恒鑌犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8a896f98cb0b7189e6f9db0bb7d76d652a4950","tid":2298983,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:03:11.000Z","msg":"自己做問卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2596b42db80fa55de96649a6734e1f34a8820f","tid":2298983,"uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"733a21cbc82944c3e125ab70ffec90cd6776a410","tid":2298983,"uid":11291,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:03:01.000